<br>
The idea behind the defense pet I was talking about is that it would not deal ANY damage at all but do other things to insure that the mob pays attention to just it and not you.<br>
<br>
Some other ideas on how this could work and not be the pet that you would always use for soloing is this.<br>
<br>
Cast time of 1-2 seconds and maybe long recast? Cost no reagent and...<br>
<br>
Pet could do massive &quot;Phantom&quot; damage to a mob to be #1 on hate list. <br>
<br>
Pet would only live for 10 seconds the suicide. Enough time to sit, mem gate and gate.<br>
<br>
<br>
Euphorion,<br>
<br>
I would limit any sort of Self Transport that a Mage got to an &quot;elemental type place&quot;. Give magicians 4 of these or maybe 4 lesser and 4 major at different levels and not level 60 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Like...<br>
<br>
Fire:    Lesser = Lavastorm,             Greater = Skyfire<br>
Water: Lesser = Dagnors Cauldron,  Greater = Colbalt Scar<br>
Earth:  Lesser = West Karana,         Greater =  Stonebrunt<br>
Air:      Lesser = Great Divide,         Greater = Plane of Air<br>
<br>
That covers all continents with a large amount of the substance used for the Gate....though Great Divide was more of a convience and pre established port.<br>
<br>
The PoA port could still cost the Airstone if needed.<br>
<br>
I left out Luclin because there are no ports there at all yet, otherwise i'd have greater water port you to Twilight Sea by Transon's Castle.<br>
<br>
I think the bandages we summon should do the following and Mages should be changed this way too..<br>
<br>
Mage Bind Wound Skill - New cap at 150, allows to bind to 65% and heals 35/bandage instead of 25.<br>
<br>
Bandages summon with +10% to bind wounds and heal an additional 10 hp/bandage.<br>
<br>
Soo a Magician could with the bandages cap skill at 160, heal up to 75%, bind for 45 hp per bandage which I belive takes 2 ticks per bind?<br>
<br>
With max aa skill in bind wounds your cap would be 95% without the bandages and 100% with them.<br>
